# Title: Invoke-Obfuscation VAR+ Launcher - System
# Author: Jonathan Cheong, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-15
# Level: high
# Description: Detects Obfuscated use of Environment Variables to execute PowerShell
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1027, attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/system/service_control_manager/win_system_invoke_obfuscation_var_services.yml

EventID=7045 ImagePath IN ("*/c*", "*/r*") ImagePath="*cmd*" ImagePath="*\"set*" ImagePath="*-f*" Provider_Name="Service Control Manager"